Class InstructionArrayExt

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.faizsiegeln.njams.messageformat.command.Instruction
      • com.faizsiegeln.njams.messageformat.command.InstructionExt
        • com.faizsiegeln.njams.messageformat.command.InstructionArrayExt
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    BasicCommand

    public class InstructionArrayExt
extends InstructionExt
    This class extends InstructionExt by functionality for storing string arrays (lists respectively) as parameter values.
    This extension provides methods for setting and getting according arrays or lists, and for removing them from the underlying instruction.
    All methods exits for both message parts, request and response.
    Author:
    cwinkler
